São Paulo - Brazil - Penitenciária - Hostage Rescue

Counter-Terrorists: Penitentiary in armed rebellion, 
four hostages. Prepare the invasion to complex 
and rescue the hostages for the helicopter.

Terrorists: Prevent Counter-Terrorist
force from rescuing the hostages.
